I mean, parang hindi mo ako naaalala.

00:17:29.830 --> 00:17:32.040
Paumanhin, hindi kita lubos na mailagay...

00:17:32.170 --> 00:17:34.290
Tumulong ako sa ilang mga proyekto ng film club.

00:17:34.420 --> 00:17:38.080
Pero naaalala kita,
Mihara. Senior ka sa kolehiyo.

00:17:38.210 --> 00:17:41.000
Lagi kong iniisip na napaka-charming mo.

00:17:41.130 --> 00:17:43.790
talaga? Ang sarap pakinggan.

00:17:43.920 --> 00:17:46.790
Well, nag-iwan ka ng malaking impression sa akin, Shirasaki.

00:17:46.920 --> 00:17:48.830
Dahil marami akong narinig tungkol sayo kay Hayama.

00:17:48.960 --> 00:17:49.670
ha?

00:17:49.790 --> 00:17:51.250
Ano nga ulit...?

00:17:51.380 --> 00:17:54.460
Diba may nasabi ka
nung na-scout siya ng modelling agency?

00:17:54.960 --> 00:17:55.830
Hayama,

00:17:55.960 --> 00:17:57.920
wala ka bang gagawing acting?

00:17:58.040 --> 00:17:59.630
Ano ang mali sa iyo?

